Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是初期開髮型試作0號機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SKYKNIGHT和FIREBRAND哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了眾多受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LUXON和BRADYON的前代機體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚呢 不過現在也在定期進行保養
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼這種東西會在夏威夷基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有研究的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過更多還是為了保管資料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 正在開發的新型機也要完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機體不會再起飛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是費爾米老師開發的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難過…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mayday Mayday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mayday是國際通用的無線電通話遇難求救訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Transport Airlines 507航班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左引擎起火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求緊急降落夏威夷基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 使用2號跑道 消防隊趕快出動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是民營機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警報也沒響 應該不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏威夷基地·第5大門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是valiancer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急通知 緊急通知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人valiancer出現在基地內
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方間諜似乎已經潛入 各部隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們急的就像熱鍋上的螞蟻啊 真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也表現的著急一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就要讓您大失所望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我們去捕食獵物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽撃(はばた)け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.08,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展翅高飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:20.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ見ぬ空に　希望(ひかり)重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:20.48,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那未知的天空 將希望重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:24.00,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哀しみの重さに　負けたりしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:24.00,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不要被那沉重的悲傷壓倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:29.04,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠に響け　UNISONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:29.04,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響徹永遠吧 UNISONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が見てるその世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.67,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你眼中的那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:44.12,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな色をしてるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:44.12,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呈現出了何種顏色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.12,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Measure feeling match)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.12,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Measure feeling match)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.85,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失くす痛みなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.85,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不想去習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.74,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慣れたくはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.74,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:56.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんな夜も星はきれいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:56.19,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這種夜晚星空也是如此地美麗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手のひらからこぼれ落ちてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.80,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那從手心中慢慢滑落的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錆びれたコインのように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.76,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銹跡斑斑的硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.88,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(モドレナイ)(カエリタイ)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.88,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（無法回頭 想重新來過）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:10.11,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背中合わせのふたり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:10.11,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背靠背的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿撃(つらぬ)け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.24,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺穿一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:16.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褪せない想い　絆に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:16.80,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不褪色的思念 轉變成為永久的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.22,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色のない世界を塗り替えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.22,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了將那無色的世界重新塗過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,届け　このシンパシー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.94,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請傳達到吧 這個共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Growing the wing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.29,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Growing the wing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:29.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想い通りの　未来を創ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:29.24,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來創造 夢想中的未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.31,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運命さえ　変えてゆける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.31,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是命運 我們也能改變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:37.44,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時を越えて　UNISONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:37.44,OPZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越時空思念 UNISONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:44.92,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(1106,589)}真實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是父親的臉 我在課堂上畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也誇我畫得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去念士官學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為保護祖國佐基利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護居住在這個國家的人民的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像父親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏威夷基地·第7裝備樓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我們詳細的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你們在廣播中聽到的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在敵軍士兵侵入到了基地內部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各處進行破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到的valiancer有8台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔基姆 差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還沒玩夠 不過沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中兩台脫離上空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停靠整備場似乎正發生槍擊戰 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白敵人的目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為侵入如此規模的基地 就只有8台valiancer哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算問司令部該如何應對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是一邊倒的告訴我們「打倒敵人 保護基地」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因此 我們採取獨自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾維拉君和小真由立刻回到艦內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉君和迪奧去回收搬入基地第7裝備樓的LUXON和BRADYON
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛姆君擔任他們倆的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道敵人會藏在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的話 就自己保護好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艙門就這麼開著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要花費點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在交戰 大概能堅持住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 啟動安全保護的解除一完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就開始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得聯繫啊 告訴佐基利亞 雛在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那樣的話 雛就會成為我們的俘虜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己的基地還真是亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐為少佐包紮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和別動隊會合 確保退路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點止血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要告訴你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會影響到傷口的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛 你並不是我的親生女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被分開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從這邊的路去目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到迂迴路過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:08:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被配屬到激戰地薩格勒布的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被燒光的戰場 遇到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的你穿著破破爛爛的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎不能說話 失去了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能記住的只有雛這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你當做戰爭孤兒領了回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 我和你成為了父女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你突然告訴我這樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀕死之人 是不會開玩笑說這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊 不能再繼續讓佐基利亞為所欲為了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敵人來之前 逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話父親也跟我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後就讓我作為一個父親耍下帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一 還是給他一槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不解風情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正沉浸在和女兒的回憶中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你們一起去地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爆炸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我只是個高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算突然讓我開槍也開不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這裡是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是我的親生女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能記住的只有雛這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你帶我來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你是我的同班同學 叫弓原雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 她在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛？你怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說入侵的敵軍士兵是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…並不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是什麼人 是青葉所說的雛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐他？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 在我離開的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎沒被捲入爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你打算去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面自動進行就會結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找雛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 里亞贊少佐他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰可以繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會有推遲 還在估計範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼接下來現場的指揮就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也會按照預定開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在把作戰成功當做最優先考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我是青葉所說的雛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 失憶的事也多少能理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不明白為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊吧 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我們這裡 到Cygnus來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也接納了從70年前來的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是敵人 只要說清楚大家一定會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也有值得信賴的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫迪奧 雖然有點臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連自己是誰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛就是雛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是一直生活在這裡的雛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是和我是同班同學的雛都沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛就是雛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會毫無保留地接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那傢伙身邊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛 你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼要袒護他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛 你不是佐基利亞的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來一起戰鬥至今的我們 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里亞贊少佐 並不是為了讓你做那樣的事才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連父親也要背叛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別追了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛姆 把那個笨蛋拉到一旁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下再說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快安全保護的解除就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務是奪取聯合的新型valiancer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上似乎安靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把上空的兩台打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 要在他們落下來之前好好揍一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷達感應 出現多數熱源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nectar屏障展開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大限度擴展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓他們落入基地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這是幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不攻佔基地 而是打算破壞？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人坐在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊落它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比被敵人奪走要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛坐在那上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊落什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道現在發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是雛所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛現在很煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她父親去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得自己不知道自己是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是能做這種事的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在聯結機…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想打落那樣的雛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們打落的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉同學和迪奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們無法用聯結系統
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機體非常危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 艾維拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把兩台機體的遠程訪問優先權轉給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要讓他們無法聯結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白我們的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是奪回LUXON和BRADYON而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上 連接迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SKYKNIGHT和FIREBRAND聯結成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能給 這種設定為什麼還能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 座艙不同 行動也不方便了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛來了哦 是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛 你坐在那個上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 現在還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從雛身邊滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 只有你這傢伙我要在這裡殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆的emphatier波形！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰目的達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始回收
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體機體在抵達合流地點前分散開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多的戰鬥行為是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 BUDDY COMPLEX 二人之絆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:41.82,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(630,486)}下回「二人之絆」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:25.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で呼ぶ　惹かれあう彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:25.23,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心的呼應 響應的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:33.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛みの理由(わけ)も忘れて　今だけどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:33.88,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛的理由 請暫且忘記 我在此深深祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:43.08,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミを知っている　キミを探しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:43.08,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深知你 我在一直尋找著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:51.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引き止められない光の残像に　そっとくちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:51.80,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕吻向那已飄渺的光的殘像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:00.81,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躊躇いが僅かな　希望への糸口なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:00.81,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那稍稍的猶豫不決 成為了那連接希望的蛛絲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:09.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨った数だけ　優しい朝へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:09.52,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那微微的彷徨 拉近了與那溫柔黎明的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:18.56,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空に還る未来で　救いたい　守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:18.56,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去拯救 想去保護 那早已歸還於天空的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その夢に届く未来で　待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.44,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請留步 那已經早已傳達過夢想的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:34.86,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと出会える愛に　手を伸ばして欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:34.86,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能與我一起去抓住 那注定相遇的愛